{"tid":1085550,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【好溫馨】陳浩民孻女3歲生日 送咪唱兒歌發揮潛能","createTime":"2019-03-31T08:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T10:27:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e32e67b5aeae72d736370073f760deba6c711b3","tid":1085550,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"49歲的「多仔公」陳浩民和太太蔣麗莎長女 （Lisa）育有三女一子，分別是7歲多長女陳雅薷（Elizabeth）、5歲多二子陳璟逸（Cyrus）、4歲多三女陳若嫣（Isabella）和昨日生日的3歲幼女陳熙妏（Victoria），一家六口樂融融。<br />\nLisa昨日在facebook貼出為孻女慶生相片，全家陪壽星女Victoria切蛋糕，Victoria高舉三隻手指示意自己已三歲。另又有一輯全家福照片，他們身穿白色家庭裝，全家圍攏齊齊玩玩具，陳浩民還拿着小結他彈奏，Victoria則戴上小皇冠扮可愛公主，她跟兩位姐姐一樣遺傳了媽咪長腿。陳浩民今日在電話回覆《蘋果》時說：「今年囡囡生日最別係安排咗佢去學整蛋糕，佢整番自己個生日蛋糕呀，Victoria好鍾意唱歌，我買咗一支玩具咪送畀佢，支咪有啲兒歌喺裏邊，咁佢可以跟住唱。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/large/1554019407_3be4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Flarge%2F1554019407_3be4.jpg&h=515b07bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/large/1554019425_0711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Flarge%2F1554019425_0711.jpg&h=71e8434e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/large/1554019425_6a81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Flarge%2F1554019425_6a81.jpg&h=81f4c959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190331/59433542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F59433542&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=2b0e4578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F59433542&h=313dc9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190331/59433542</a>"},{"pid":"b3d6440510746044e7a178824b5e8c6f171fdb79","tid":1085550,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"Pokemon!"},{"pid":"ca7e1ea8919e82559300d7f9bd11dfc5d739f1e7","tid":1085550,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>49歲的「多仔公」陳浩民和太太蔣麗莎<span style=\"color: red;\">長女</span> （Lisa）<span style=\"color: red;\">育有三女一子</span>，分別是7歲多長女陳雅薷（Elizabeth）、5歲多二子陳璟逸（Cyrus）、4歲多三女陳若嫣（Isabella）和昨日生日的3歲幼女陳熙妏（Victoria），一家六口樂融融。</blockquote><br />\n7歲長女育有三女一子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a54f6bad22bf76996b54c1b2167d6455a420eb9","tid":1085550,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca7e1ea8919e82559300d7f9bd11dfc5d739f1e7","tid":1085550,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>49歲的「多仔公」陳浩民和太太蔣麗莎<span style=\"color: red;\">長女</span> （Lisa）<span style=\"color: red;\">育有三女一子</span>，分別是7歲多長女陳雅薷（Elizabeth）、5歲多二子陳璟逸（Cyrus）、4歲多三女陳若嫣（Isabella）和昨日生日的3歲幼女陳熙妏（Victoria），一家六口樂融融。</blockquote><br />\n7歲長女育有三女一子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}